Issue 1: Implement Word Modification Features

@mrjoswald-avenues

1. Capitalize word
a) create a function that capitalizes word 
b) implement logic to capitalize the first letter of the word
c) add UI option to apply this modification

2. Subsitute Letters
a) create a function to subsitute letters
b) define a dictionary of letter-to-symbol things (like @ for a or $ for s)
c) implement logic to replace letters with corresponding symbols
d) add a UI option to apply this modification

3. Append A Number
a) create a function to do so
b) implement logic to add a random number from 0 to 9 to the end of the word
c) add a UI option to apply this modification
